={
  "type": "Email",
  "contactId": "{{ $json.leadId }}",
  "subject": "Welcome to Our Landscaping Services!",
  "html": "{{ $('Generate Personalized Follow-Up Message').first().json.message }}"
}

={
  "type": "SMS",
  "contactId": "{{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.leadId }}",
  "message": "Hi {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.leadName }}, we sent you an email about your {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.serviceType }} inquiry. Please check your inbox or reply here!"
}

parameters.text:
=🌱 New Lead Alert!

*Name:* {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.leadName }}
*Service:* {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.serviceType }}
*Phone:* {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.leadPhone }}
*Email:* {{ $('Normalize Lead Information').first().json.leadEmail }}
*Status:* {{ $json.Status }}

Messages sent: SMS + Email

=📊 Weekly Lead Summary Report

*Total Leads:* {{ $json.length }}
*Emails Opened:* {{ $json.filter(l => l["Email Opened"] === "Yes").length }}
*Follow-ups Scheduled:* {{ $json.filter(l => l.Status === "Follow-up Scheduled").length }}
*Reminders Sent:* {{ $json.filter(l => l.Status === "Reminder Sent").length }}

Keep up the great work! 🚀
